ist 31.5pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">6、<SPAN style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">期末统计学生干部考核结果，每学期开学第二周星期一前将学生干部附加分情况送各班班长处。<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><U><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">寝室长：</SPAN></U></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"> <B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><U><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></U></B></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 35.95pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: -1.5; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">1、负责掌握本室同学的思想动态，以寝室为单位组织开展丰富多彩有意义<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN>的活动，促进室友之间的团结，以形成良好寝室风气。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo13; tab-stops: 18.0pt list 36.0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">2、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">负责制定本室内务整理值日制度，并督促同学认真履行，。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo13; tab-stops: list 36.0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">3、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">负责引导和组织本室成员积极开展争先创优活动。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo13; tab-stops: list 36.0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">4、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">积极配合班卫生委员，系卫生部的工作并定期将工作情况向班委会汇报。<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '规章制度', '学生管理', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2005-06-14 00:00:00', '1866', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('52', '人文社科系青年志愿者\'服务队成立计划', '<DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文行楷; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">人文社科系青年志愿者服务队成立计划</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 华文行楷\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 华文行楷\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人文社科，顾名思义，关注社会，重视人性与个性的和谐统一。为了使本系更加充满人文色彩，使本系活动开展得有声有色，决定成立青年志愿者服务队。青年志愿者服务队，将会用真心、诚心关爱生活在我们身边的每一个人，用我们力所能及的一切给同学们提供帮助和服务，用实际行动树立本系大学生的鲜明形象。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">首先，青年志愿者服务队成员的招募必须建立在自愿原则的基础上，成员必须要有良好的思想道德素质，强烈的责任感和乐于奉献的精神，党员必须充分发挥其优势，起带头作用。整个队的宗旨是全心全意为同学们服务。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">其次，青年志愿者服务队成立的对象为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">02</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">03</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">04</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">级同学，组成成员大约</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">30</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人（男女搭配协调）。大一每班</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">7</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人，大二每班</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">6</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人，大三每班</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">再次，青年志愿者服务队成立的具体过程如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">①</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日中午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">12</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">请</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">02</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">03</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">04</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">级班级团支书在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">503</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">开会，传达成立青年志愿者服务队即将成立这一消息，并领取“青年志愿者服务队报名登记表“。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">②</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">团支书监督各位同学把表格填写好并于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">21</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日，务必把表格递交上来。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; tab-stops: 18.0pt 27.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">③4月22日，本部门将从所上交的表格中进行筛选，并选出队长及队长助理（男女各一名），负责本队日常工作的运行。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">最后，为了使青年志愿者服务队更好的为同学们服务，特明确成员所应履行的义务和享受的权利：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">义务：①开展一切活动时，以本系和大多数同学的利益为出发点。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; mso-char-indent-count: -3.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>②遵守学校及本系各项制度，积极并且乐意地听从部们的安排和调遣，如果不积极配合本系活动的顺利进行，将实行扣分处理，严重者从青年志愿者服务队除名。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; mso-char-indent-count: -3.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">权利 ：<SPAN lang=EN-US>①凡是青年志愿者服务队的成员在其综合测评分上每人每期加0.2分了，并且在此基础上根据成员在以后工作过程中的参与程度与积极性，适当的进行加分，每次加0.1分。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>②在干部提拔或评选中，青年志愿者服务队成员将会作为优先考察的对象。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; TEXT-INDENT: -336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>组织部</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; TEXT-INDENT: -336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>2005年4月20日<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '学生工作', '计划总结', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2005-06-14 00:00:00', '1105', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('53', '人文社科系寝室“温馨”规则', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">人文社科系寝室“温馨”规则<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">为了创建文明和谐宿舍，为同学提供良好的学习生活环境，特别制定此规则：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">一：学习方面<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">注重寝室学风建设，学风浓，学习你追我赶，互相帮助，达到全面提高。不定期的开展学习心得交流；围绕某个热点开展自由的辩论，以提高语言表达能力；在交流、辩论的同时，互相吸收与时俱进的观点，以便开阔思维、拓宽视野。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">二：作息方面<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">周一至周五：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 17.7pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.47; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">6：00 -6:10<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>起床</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN>8：00－11:40 上课或自习 <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN>12:00-14:20　午休<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">14:30-18:00　 上课或自习<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">19:30-22:30<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>自习时间<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">　 <B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>22:30-23:00<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>清点人数，洗漱，准备睡觉</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">三：卫生方面<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BACKGROUND: silver; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-highlight: silver\">①</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">地面干净</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">(</SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">注</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">:</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">地面无烟头，无纸屑其他杂物，床底下整洁</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">)</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">②</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">鞋子摆放一条线</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">③</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">桌凳干净（注：桌子、凳子干净）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">④</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">门窗（窗户和窗台）玻璃无灰尘</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（注：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">门擦干净、玻璃擦干净，窗台、窗户擦干净。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">⑤</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">床上用品摆放整齐（注：枕头、枕巾不乱放，床上衣服不乱挂）。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">⑥</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">天花板干净，电话机灯座无灰尘（注：天花板无蜘蛛网等脏物，电话机无灰尘，灯座无灰尘）。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">⑦</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">洗漱用品摆放整洁并整齐</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（注：桶里无未洗的衣服、袜子，毛巾摆放整齐；杯子、牙刷、牙膏摆放统一）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">四：生活手册<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">1、不准在寝室里说脏话、粗话，注意个人形象。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">2、不准在寝室里喝酒，吸烟。3、严禁在宿舍里赌博，打麻将；<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">4、不准在寝室里大声喧哗，起哄，打架斗殴，互相辱骂；<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">5、周一至周五不得在寝室里打牌,下象棋、围棋等；（文体活动时间和晚餐后除外）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">6、不得在室内使用电热杯，热得快等各种大功率电器；<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>7、不准夜不归宿，不准留宿外人；<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">8、不准破坏公共财产。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">五：寝室铭<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体\">山不在高，有仙则名；水不在深，有龙则灵。斯是吾室，唯物得馨；苔痕上阶绿，草色入帘青。谈笑有吾辈，往来无他辈；可以调素琴，览群书。无吵闹之乱耳，无喧骂之牢神；南阳诸葛庐，西蜀子云亭。孔子云：何乐之有！<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P></DIV>', '学生工作', '工作安排', '0', null, '人文社会科学', '2005-06-14 00:00:00', '1325', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('54', '人文社科系创建和谐宿舍活动一', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人文社科系创建和谐宿舍活动一：</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">和谐示范宿舍评比细则</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">为创建我系和谐示范宿舍，起到以点带面的作用，男女生部特别制定本次活动的评比细则，具体情况如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一、和谐示范宿舍温馨设计（</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">20</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、宿舍内统一张帖墙纸。（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、科学合理搭配，内容健康，思想积极上进的字、画、图。（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、宿舍配有自己的“照出自信之镜”。（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、宿舍内扎有剪纸等富有创新的物品。（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、宿舍设计突出人文特色，保持个性色彩。（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二、内务大比拼（</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">35</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">，日常检查（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）（开学至第十二周）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日常检查：基本分</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">12</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分（未奖未罚得分），</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">个人被好</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">/</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">差（一次一人</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">+/-0.2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分），</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">宿舍内务好差（一次</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">+/-0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分），</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">最高分不超过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">，特别检查（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">15</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）（按</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">100</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分制计分，再折合成</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">15</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BACKGROUND: silver; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-highlight: silver\">①</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">地面干净（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">15</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">地面有烟头一个扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，有纸屑扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，床底不整洁扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，整体效果占</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">②</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">鞋子分类摆放整齐（一条线）（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一双鞋子乱扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，以此类推，整体效果占</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">③</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">桌凳干净，桌面整齐（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">15</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一张桌子或凳子乱扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，不干净分别扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，书本摆放不整齐扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，最低分</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">④</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">门窗（窗户和窗台）玻璃无灰尘（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">门未擦干净扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，未擦扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分；玻璃</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">—</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">块未擦干净扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，过半数未擦干净扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分；窗台、窗户未擦干净</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">—</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">处扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">基本未擦扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">⑤</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">床上用品摆放整齐（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">枕头（枕巾）乱放一个扣</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1