s New Roman\'\">分，最高分不超过</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">15</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）（以一学年为期）</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">1，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">宿舍成员在系院活动（如：演讲比赛、象棋比赛、文艺比拼）中获奖的，一等奖加</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分每次，二等奖加</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分每次，三等奖加</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分每次，优胜奖加</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分每次。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">2，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">宿舍组织策划相关有影响有意义的活动加</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">五、材料准备（</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">15</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）坚持求真务实、创新的原则进行。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">1，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">思想与实践（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）：努力学习马列主义、毛泽东思想、邓小平理论和“三个代表”重要思想</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，寝室有三个以上参加入党的相关培训，以证书复印件为准</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分；考试无舞弊现象</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，与本专业有关的实践经验</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">0.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">2，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">宿舍生活（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）：有体现室友关系的内容</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，日常生活简介</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，活动计划、总结</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分，活动相关照片（如室内设计照片、活动照片等）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">3，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">特色个人简介（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）介绍优秀个人事迹。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">4，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">受表彰情况（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">4.5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分）（附获奖证书复印件，以</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2004</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">下学期至</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2005</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">年上学期为时间段），依据复印件准备情况按比例计分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人文社科系男女生部</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>2005-4-20<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2005-06-14 00:00:00', '1357', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('55', '人文系首届班级篮球比赛策划书', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文行楷\">人文系首届班级篮球比赛策划书<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">活动名称：人文系首届“人文杯”班级篮球联赛</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">活动目的：选拔篮球人才，丰富全系同学业余文化生活，增强各班班集体凝聚力</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">活动宗旨：友谊第一，比赛第二。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">活动时间：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">2005</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">年上学期第八周星期三至第九周星期五</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">活动地点：师院体育馆外篮球场</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">参赛对象：人文系肄业班全体学生</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">活动细则：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一、各班派出有八名男队员和八名女队员分别组成班级男、女篮球队以班级的名义参加比赛，各队需着统一篮球服，服装整齐，并需在上衣统一印有号码。各队还需确定队长一名，由队长负责监督队员参加比赛。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二、比赛第一轮采用小组内循环赛制，即由各班体育委员以抽签的形式决定分组，细分</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">A</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">B</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">两组，每组三个队，小组内循环互赛，决出小组前两名进入第二轮比赛。在第二轮比赛中，由</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">A</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">组的第一名对战</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">B</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">组第二名，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">A</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">组第二名对战</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">B</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">组第一名。胜出双方直接进入总决赛，其余两对争夺第三名。在小组比赛时，若三队获胜次数相同，则以净胜球多少排定名次。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">三、本次篮球赛竞赛规则按照中国篮协近年制定的竞赛规则执行。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">四、活动奖励：本次比赛取前三名，给予相应的物质和精神奖励。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">五、经过各班体育委员抽签，分组情况如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <TABLE class=MsoTableGrid style=\"BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; BORDER-TOP: medium none; MARGIN: auto auto auto 140.4pt; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-yfti-tbllook: 480; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; mso-border-insideh: .5pt solid windowtext; mso-border-insidev: .5pt solid windowtext\" cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 border=1> <TBODY> <TR style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 0\"> <TD style=\"BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 59.25pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\" vAlign=top width=79> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>A</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">组</SPAN></P></TD> <TD style=\"BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: #ece9d8; WIDTH: 57.75pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm