AN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、人的懒惰性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">…………………………………………………</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、希望捡钱的心理分析</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">………………………………………</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、差异</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">…………………………………………………………</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.