style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">……………………………………………</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、专制主义下的个人意志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">……………………………………</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、动物只求生，人则求利</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">………………………………………</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、个体的人的内容</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">……………………………………………</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</