height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">组长：刘余香<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">成员：唐云红、宋建丽、何良娥、滕召艳、曾莉平<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>6）后勤服务组</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">组长：苏盛敏<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">成员：肖永华、付湘、谢益军<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>7）、校风、学风、舍风迎检组：<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">组长： 陈君生<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">成员：苏盛敏、各班班主任、王凯、毛润军、夏实<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">二、各工作小组工作职责<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">1、材料组：<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">廖建平：综合汇报材料文字稿、课件制作、汇报与答疑；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">唐林生：资料室汇报材料文字稿、汇报与答疑；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">陈君生：迎接自评工作方案、迎评工作日程安排表；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">2、毕业论文、试卷、教案抽查迎检组</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">毕业论文按年度专业整理，试卷按学期、专业、课程整理，教案放教师个人档案。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">3、宣传报道组</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">网页更新，横幅张挂，汇报投影器材调试，汇报会摄像、摄影，文字通迅报道等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">4、联络组</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">听取学院迎评办公室安排，联系召开座谈会教师与学生等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">5、会务接待组</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">买水果、礼仪接待、倒茶水等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">6、后勤服务组</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN>打扫会议室卫生，搬材料合子等。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">7、校风、学风、舍风迎检组<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoBodyTextIndent style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt\"><FONT face=仿宋_GB2312>召开动员会，校风、学风、舍风检查，其中主要检查课堂纪律、宿舍卫生、风纪和日常行为风尚等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">三、迎接学院自评具体工作与要求<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">1、专家走访系部：<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">一是听取系领导汇报。系主任作综合汇报（不超过<SPAN lang=EN-US>18分钟），副主任作资料室情况汇报（不超过3分钟）。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">二是查看系评估材料和考证相关数据。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">三是提出问题。由系汇报人答疑。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">综合汇报主要包括系基本情况、专业设置、教学科研等基本情况、主要特色和亮点等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">资料室汇报主要包括基本条件、建设情况、图书资料的结构、数量及使用情况等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">2、召开座谈会<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">召开座谈会前，由专家组根据名册随机抽调，再由联络员分块通知系部（ 教师座谈会由教务处负责通知、组织，管理人员座谈会由人事处负责通知、组织，学生座谈会由学生工作处负责通知、组织），然后由系部负责通知到人。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">参加座谈会的学生、教师、干部必须在座谈会召开前<SPAN lang=EN-US>10分钟到达指定的会场。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">参会人员注意会场纪律，不准吸烟、讲小话，关闭手机，积极思考，有问必答，不问不答。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">3、随机听课<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">专家组成员主要集中在<SPAN lang=EN-US>6月21日上午、23日下午听课，其余时间听课可由专家根据工作需要自行安排。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">自评期间，系工作人员按作息时间提前<SPAN lang=EN-US>5-10分钟上班，推迟5-10分钟下班，教师及学生上课必须严格遵守教学纪律，提前5-10分钟到教室，不得迟到、早退。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">全校师生必须佩戴校徽。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">4、抽查毕业论文、试卷、教案<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">专家抽调的毕业论文、试卷名单先交联络员，由联络员与教务处联系，然后由教务处通知系部。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">系部由专人负责呈送相关的抽调材料，检查完后仍由该同志领回存档。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">毕业论文以<SPAN lang=EN-US>2006届学生的为主、试卷以抽查全校2005年下学期及2006年上学期毕业生试卷为主，少量抽查前两学年的毕业论文及试卷。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">专家在查阅部门评估材料时，将会少量抽查最近一学年教师的授课教案。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">6、学生技能测试<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">专家根据学生名册随机抽测，被抽查的学生名单由联络员通知教务处，然后由教务处通知相关系部，系部负责落实到学生。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">对学生的技能测试主要考察理科学生的实验操作及动手能力、师范类学生的微格教学及课堂教学能力、全校学生的计算机操作水平及英语听说能力。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">对学生进行技能测试，专家主要采取走访、随时交谈及集中测试等方式进行。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">7、专家就餐<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">21日中餐专家及联络员统一到学生食堂就餐，其余时间由专家个人自行安排，系辅导员同10名学生在专家就餐食堂吃饭。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">专家与同学交谈时，应热情、礼貌、文明，有问必答。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">8、宣传报道<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">网页必须及时反映系最新工作动态和教学及相关信息，及时报道评估的动态信息。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">宣传横幅制作与张挂。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">系迎评汇报会摄影、摄像工作。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">动态跟踪文字报道，<SPAN lang=EN-US>1小时内挂系网页，并报送学院《评估快讯》。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.05pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">9、学生工作<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">学生讲究公德，公共场所不吐痰、乱丢纸团、穿拖鞋、背心。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">宿舍卫生按军训标准，学生在专家进宿舍时主动让座、礼貌问候、倒开水。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-char-indent-size: 12.0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">早晨按时起床锻炼身体和早自习，不得睡懒觉，晚自习到教室或图书馆看书。晚上按时就寝，不得打牌、打游戏，不得晚归。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">三、迎评工作方针与总的要求<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">1、方针：</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">以评促建、以评促改、以评促管，评建结合，重在建设。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">2、总的要求</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">一是加强领导，落实岗位责任；二是提高认识，高度重视；三是积极参与，发挥各自主人翁精神。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt\">按学院要求做到“五个‘一’”：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt\">全院一盘棋，按工作方案统一调度、统一指挥；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt\">上下一条心，按实战要求精心准备、严阵以待；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt\">拧成一股绳，既找差距、查漏洞，又要不断总结经验，起到凝聚人心、鼓舞士气的作用；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt\">突出一中心，按本科教学工作水平评估教育部专家组现场考察要求，全方位检查教学中心地位是否得到充分体现，考察我院的“三个符合度”；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt\">追求一目标，按评建工作<SPAN lang=EN-US>20字方针，积极开展自评自建，确保我院评建目标的实现，不断提升教学质量。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>人文社会科学系<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>2006年6月18日</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV>', '近期工作', '本站通知', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2006-06-21 00:00:00', '1280', '0');
