:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">3. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">把握共产主义道德品质的本质特点。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 20.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.97\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 20.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.97\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 20.7pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.97\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第十一章</SPAN> <SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">道德评价</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">考试内容</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">行为善恶的责任、评价行为的标准和根据、道德评价的类型、手段和作用。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">考试要求</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">1. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">理解人们行为善恶的责任问题；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">2. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">理解道德行为过程中动机与效果的辩证统一关系；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">3. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">把握道德评价并理解社会的道德评价和自我道德评价的特点和相互关系；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">4. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">理解在道德评价中，社会舆论、内心信念和传统习惯的作用。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 20.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第十二章</SPAN> <SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">道德教育与道德修养</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">考试内容</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">共产主义道德教育的社会作用、道德教育的一般过程、道德教育的基本特征、道德教育的主要方法和手段、道德教育中需要正确处理的几种关系、道德修养的可能性和必要性、道德修养的实质、道德修养的根本途径、道德境界的含义和客观基础。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">考试要求</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">1. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">把握道德教育过程的基本环节、特征、方法；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">2. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">正确理解道德修养是可能的和必要的；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">4. </SPAN><SPAN style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">正确理解道德境界的含义。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">四、考试的方法和考试时间</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">本课程采用闭卷考试，考试时间为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>120</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分钟。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">五、评价标准</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">学生修完本课程并参加期末考试后，以其期末考试的成绩为准。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">六、试卷设计的结构</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">试卷题型为填空题、辨析题、名词解释、简答题、论述题。其中客观题与主观题约各占</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>50%</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '伦理学', '考试大纲与教学进度计划', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2007-04-12 00:00:00', '1209', '0');
