OM: windowtext 1pt solid; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\" vAlign=top width=187> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">施于人<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></TD> <TD style=\"BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: #ece9d8; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: #ece9d8; WIDTH: 108pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\" vAlign=top width=144> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">可能恶<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></TD> <TD style=\"BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: #ece9d8; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: #ece9d8; WIDTH: 99pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt\" vAlign=top width=132> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">可能恶<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">从上表中可以清楚地看到</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律即“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”的道德性最明确</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也最容易掌握</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">具有很强的可操作性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而其它任何一条准则的道德性都不如金律这么明确</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">都不便于掌握和操作。而且</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律的这种道德性是每个人心中自明的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">凭着自己的体会就可以直观地感受到它的正确性。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">拉·梅特里把道德金律称之为“自然法则”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">并明确地指明了道德金律的自明性。他说</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">:</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“现在我们怎样给这个自然的法则下定义呢</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我们说</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这是一种感觉</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">它告诉我们‘己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人’。甚至</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在这个一般的概念之上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我还敢添加一句</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">:</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这种感觉不是别的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">只是一种害怕或恐惧</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但却是一种对于整个的种属和个体都很有益的害怕或恐惧。因为如果不是为保全自己的财产、名誉和生命</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我们也许就不那么尊重别人的钱包和生命了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">正像那些基督教的伊克雄们一样</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">如果不是因为害怕地狱</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也许就不那么热爱上帝</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也不肯遵守那么一大套幻想的道德教条了。“因此</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">大家可以看到</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">所谓自然的法则只是一种内在的感觉</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">它和其他一切内在感觉一样</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">(</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">其中也包括思想</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">)</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">仍然只是一种属于想像作用的作用。因此自然的法则是既不需要教育</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也不需要启示</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也不需要什么立法者的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">除非我们和神学家一样可笑</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">把自然的法则和社会的法律混为一谈了。”</SPAN><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 5.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">④</SPAN></SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 5.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">从拉·梅特里的这段话中可以看到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">:</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律的自我澄明不是先验的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而是社会历史和文化的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这种自我澄明来源于对人的需要的正确理解</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“是一种对于整个的种属和个体都很有益的害怕和恐惧”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">否则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">所谓的自我澄明就会成为虚无缥渺、不可捉摸的东西。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">总之</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律作为一条道德准则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是根源于人性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">发端于对人共同性和差异性的辩证认识</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">并能在人们心目中自我澄明的一条道德性最为显明的道德准则。它不愧于人们称之为道德金律</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是最起码、最基本的道德准则。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">注释<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">①陈立夫</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">四书道贯·致知篇·知性<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">②周辅成</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">西方伦理学名著选辑上卷</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">第</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">251</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">页</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">商务印书馆</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，<SPAN lang=EN-US>1996</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">③罗国杰</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">什么是中华民族优良道德传统</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人民日报</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，<SPAN lang=EN-US>1994</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">23</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">日<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">④拉·梅特里</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人是机器</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">第</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">46</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">～</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">47</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">页</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">商务印书馆</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 7.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，<SPAN lang=EN-US>1996</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">年<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '伦理学', '论文与学术报告', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2007-04-13 00:00:00', '497', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('202', '道德金律的哲学阐释（第一部分）', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">廖建平<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">[</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">摘<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>要<SPAN lang=EN-US>]</SPAN>“己所不欲，勿施于人”这条道德金律根源于人性，它在承认每个人都有欲望的前提下，既强调要尊重他人欲望，又强调不要把自己的欲望强加到别人头上。它发端于人己异同的辩证认识，是在正确理解人的需要和人的共同性、差异性的基础上提出的道德准则，人与人是可以相通的，把我所不欲的强行施于人，那就可能造成对别人的伤害，因为，我所不欲的，也可能是别人所不欲的，因此<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>“己所不欲，勿施于人”，内蕴着“人所不欲，勿施于人”，道德金律也有利于防止貌似正确的“人所欲，施于人”的错误准则的滥觞。这一道德准则具有最明显的道德性，并能在人们的心目中自我澄明。它最容易掌握和最容易操作，人们凭着自己的体验就可以直观地感受到它的正确性。它确实是最起码、最基本的道德准则。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">[</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">关键词<SPAN lang=EN-US>] </SPAN>道德金律；人性论基础；认识论前提；自明性<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">1993</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">8</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">28</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">日至</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">9</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">日</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">召开的“世界宗教议会”大会上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">讨论、通过并签署的《走向全球伦理普世宣言》</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">提出了全球伦理的构想</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">并把“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”作为其中最为基本的道德戒律</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这一戒律</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">被世人称之为道德金律或黄金规则。虽然事实上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">全球伦理中还提出了“四不可”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">即“不可杀人”、“不可盗窃”、“不可撒谎”、“不可奸淫”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也包括了耶稣所说的“你们愿意别人怎么对待你们</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">你们也要怎样待他们”。但我认为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这些规范在逻辑上都不过是“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”的具体化和进一步推论。因此</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律就是“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”。这一金律看上去只是一个极其简单的道德常识</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但它却是世界各主要文化类型的共同的最为基本的道德准则。为什么世界各主要文化类型都会不约而同地确认这一简单的道德准则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">为什么《走向全球伦理普世宣言》一公开</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就在世界范围内引起如此深广的影响</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">以至于超出宗教学的范围</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">迅速地影响到伦理学、哲学、政治学、经济学等多个学科领域</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这些现象背后必有值得探讨的重大的根源性理由。而要探讨这些理由</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就必须对道德金律本身作出充分的学理阐析。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-outline-level: 1\" align=center><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">一、尊重欲望</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">：</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律的人性论基础<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">欲与不欲都是欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是一对社会历史性范畴</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在不同的社会历史条件下</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人们欲求什么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不欲什么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">都是与社会的生产力状况、经济发展水平、社会生产方式以及文化教育、风俗习惯等诸多因素紧密联系的。而且</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">社会越进步</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">生产力水平越高</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">生产方式越合理化</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人的欲望就会具有不断扩大的趋势。在这个意义上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">有人认为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">欲望就是需要</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在不太严格的意义上这样讲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也许并无大错</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但严格说来</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">欲望与需要是有差别的。这个差别就在于</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">需要包括人的欲望和自然需要。自然需要是人们天生具有的本能</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也就是儒家所讲的性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">陈立夫的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">:</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“性为天赋于人之生存本能”</SPAN><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 5.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">①</SPAN></SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就正好说明了这一点</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">自然需要是人的内在本能</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是必须满足的生理需求。而欲望则是扩大了的自然需要</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">它已经不是内在的本能</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而是来自身外的通过比较而膨胀起来的心理意向</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">它固然以自然需要为依据或前提</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但远远超过了自然需要</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是自然需要的放纵或扩大化。如果一个人的需要仅仅局限在满足自身的生理需要的意义上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那只能说是一种自然需要</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">比如饿了要吃饱</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">冷了要穿暖等。但是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人们在实际的生活中</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">往往并非如此</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人们饿了要吃</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但不只是吃饱而是要吃好</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">甚至要吃到挥霍浪费的地步</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">冷了要穿</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但不满足于穿暖</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而是要穿好</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">穿到足以炫耀自己</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">足以标榜自己的某种属性的地步</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这就是欲望。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">任何一种道德都是以某种人性论为基础的。而人性是不能排除人的需要的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不但不能排除人的自然需要</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也不能排除人的欲望。欲望乃是人生中的一种真实自然的存在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是人的社会性及其精神属性的表现。正是因为人有欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人类才有道德</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">才能谈道德。哪怕人们把欲望归结为恶的代名词</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">当作罪恶的渊薮</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也不能否认这个结论。这是因为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德在本质上是一种真诚的自觉自律的行为及其过程</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而不是一种蒙昧的无知无为。也就是说</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德作为一种自知的、自觉的行为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是与人的自然需要和欲望紧相关联的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人只有在有自知的欲望时</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">才能谈道德、有道德</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">如果一个人什么欲望也没有</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">结果他什么损人的事也没做</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">对他来说是没有什么道德可言的。只有自知自己的某种欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也能实现这种欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">甚至是自知自己的十分过分的欲望——想作恶</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而且也能作恶</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但自己自觉地抑制这种欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">杜绝这种欲望引起的行为发生</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">避免其消极的社会影响</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这样的行为才是道德。假使我们把蒙昧的无知无为当作道德的话</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那么毫无疑问</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">花草树木</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">甚至瓦砾沙石</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就是最有道德的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">因为它们从来没有作恶</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">从来就没有过非份之想。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">由此可见</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">尽管人们常识性地认为欲望是道德的对立物</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">以致于理学家提出要“存天理</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">灭人欲”。但实际上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">正是欲望成了滋生道德的土壤。分析道德金律的目的就是要告诉人们</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">凡人都有各种欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我们所应有的态度是要高度正视和重视人的欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而不是要否认欲望。否认了欲望也就从根本上否认了人能够成为有道德者。在一定的意义上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">正是由于人有欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人才有力量去克服自己的各种非份之想</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">成为一个有道德的人。正是因为人有欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">社会才得以不断进步。所以近代大多数思想家</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">(</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">从霍布斯到费尔巴哈</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">)</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">都认为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">蔑视欲望就是蔑视道德</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">欲望与道德具有一致性。当然</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">承认欲望是道德的原动力</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">并不意味着要放纵或贪欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而是要象苏格拉底所说的那样</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">要作欲望的主宰</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而不要作欲望的奴隶。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律所体现的原则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就是在承认每个人都有欲望的前提下</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">强调要尊重他人的欲望和谨慎地对待自己的欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不能把自己的欲望强加到别人头上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">即“己所欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而是要不忽视别人的欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">从而不损害他人的欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">即要尊守“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”的准则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">可以说</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在德性意义上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这一金律具有绝对的真理性。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-outline-level: 1\" align=center><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">二、人的共同性与差异性的统一</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">：</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律的认识论前提<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">1996</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">年《云南师范大学哲学社会科学学报》第三期上有一篇杨树森先生的文章</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">题目是《“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”道德准则的历史局限性》</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">文章认为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">:</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”是主观唯心主义世界观在个人道德行为准则上的一种表现</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这一准则“抹杀了人与人之间的个性差异</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不利于调整当代社会人与人之间的关系</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">更重要的还在于这一准则“与共产主义道德的基本原则——集体主义相违背”；并以此为由</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">主张用“人所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">人之所欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">施之于人”来替代“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">己之所欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">施之于人”的道德准则。该文作者的道德目的或本意无疑是非常善良并且崇高的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但在理论上却有值得商榷的地方。在我看来</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">对“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”这一道德金律应该作如下分析。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">第一</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">并不意味着“己所欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也不意味着“己所不欲”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就要阻止或反对“人所欲”。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在逻辑上</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">对任何一种否定性规定的否定</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">并不一定意味着对对立的肯定性规定的肯定。“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">只是强调了我所不想要的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就不要强加给别人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">即人们在行为动机上应该是善良的。因为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我之所以不想要它</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就是因为它有损于我</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">对我有害</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">如果我把这种对我有损、有害的东西强施于人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就是转嫁危机</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">嫁祸于人。因此</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在动机上就是不道德的。一种行为如失去了动机的道德性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不管这种行为的后果如何</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">其道德性都要大打折扣。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我所不欲的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就不施于人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">如果正好你所欲的是我所不欲的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我不施于你</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不帮助你</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">你可以主动地去争取、去获得</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但我不必去阻止、反对你获得</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">因为我只是不帮助你获得</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不强求你获得。这才是哲学的真精神</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“哲学使在人之中的精灵……不无目的而行事</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不虚伪而行事</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不觉到需要别人作某事或不作某事”。</SPAN><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 5.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">②</SPAN></SUP><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 5.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">第二</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律是在承认人的共同性与差异性相统一的认识基础上提出来的。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律之所以用这样一种否定性规定</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而不用肯定性规定</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">原因就在于提出道德金律</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">既要承认、肯定人与人的不同之处</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">又要承认、肯定人与人的相同之处</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">它是承认人的共同性、又尊重人的差异性的结果。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">首先</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是在肯定了人的共同性的基础上的正确的道德准则。因为我是人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">他人也是人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我所不欲的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">他人也可能不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">即所谓“人同此心</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">心同此理”。人与人是可以相通的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">通过推己及人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就可以断定</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">:</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我不能把己所不欲的施于人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">强行施于别人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就可能损害别人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就可能是一种自私、利己的行为。因此</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">已逻辑地蕴涵着“人所不欲，勿施于人”。如果没有人与人的共通性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那我们就不可能知道他人所不欲的是什么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也就不可能做出利他的行为。而正因为人们之间有这种共通性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我们才可以探知他人不欲什么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">才能避免对他人施恶。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">其次</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">也是在尊重个体差异的情况下</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">提出的相对合理的准则。人与人虽然有相同的一面</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">但也有不同之处。一方面</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我所想要的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">不一定就是别人所想要的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">相反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在某些情况下</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我所想要的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">正是别人不想要的。据此</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我们可以断定</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">:</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“己所欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">施于人”是行不通的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">正象有的父母</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">自己对音乐情有独钟</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">于是就要求自己的儿女也要学音乐</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">结果由于小孩没有兴趣</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">弄得事与愿违。事实表明</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">由于个体差异的存在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">任何一种把自己所想要的、感兴趣的东西</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">强行施之于人</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">都可能对他人造成伤害</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">主观良好的愿望不一定能取得良好的效果。另一方面</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我所不想要的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">当然也不一定是别人所不想要的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">相反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">有可能正是别人想要的。在这种情况下</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">仍然要以“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”作为道德准则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">因为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">如前文所述</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这一准则并没有要反对别人去争取“人之所欲”的意思。相反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">如果只要是他人所欲的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">就施于他人的话</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">倒是表明了自己是一个是非不分、缺乏判断力的人。对他人所欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我们不可能作一个抽象的概括并从中引申出一个道德原则来</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">而必须要对他人所欲作具体的分析。假如他人所欲是不合理的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">比如有人要吸毒、杀人、放火、偷盗、扒窃等</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">这些都是我们所不欲的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">他要这么做</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">从“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”的立场来看</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那还应该反对“他人”的这种不合理的欲望</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">因为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">他施于我时</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是我不愿的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">所以也不希望他自己去为所欲为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">更不希望他施于第三者。而在这种情况下</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">奉行“人所欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">施于人”的话</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那我们岂不正好成了歹徒的帮凶</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">一条道德准则如果这样缺乏理性的话</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">那将是极其可悲的。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">道德金律采用这样一种否定性规定</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">既有利于防止用人的共同性否认人的差异性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">又有利于防止用人的差异性否认人的共同性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">是一种极其理性的道德准则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">因此</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">罗国杰教授高度地肯定这一道德准则的积极作用</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">认为“己所不欲</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">勿施于人”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">“中国传统伦理道德中的这种人本主义道德原则</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">在长期的历史发展中</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">对于协调人际关系</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 8.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">发挥了极为重要的作用”。</SPAN><SUP><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 5.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">③<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SUP></P></DIV>', '伦理学', '论文与学术报告', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2007-04-13 00:00:00', '726', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('204', '毕业论文指导提纲', '<DIV> <DIV><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <H1 style=\"MARGIN: 17pt 0cm 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第三章</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">编写论文提纲</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H1> <H1 style=\"MARGIN: 17pt 0cm 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一、编写提纲的意义与作用</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H1> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">在毕业论文的写作过程中，指导教师一般都要求学生编写提纲。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <H2 style=\"MARGIN: 13pt 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">（一）需要编写提纲的原因：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H2> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、从写作程序上讲，它是作者动笔行文前的必要准备；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、从提纲本身来讲，它是作者构思谋篇的具体体现。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">毕业论文的写作不像写诗、散文、札记那样，随感而发，信手拈来，用一则材料、几段短语就表达一种思想、一种感情；而是要用大量的资料，较多的层次，严密的推理来展开论述，从各个方面来阐述理由、论证自己的观点。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">因此，构思谋篇就显得非常重要，于是必须编制写作提纲，以便有条理地安排材料、展开论证。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <H2 style=\"MARGIN: 13pt 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">（二）编写提纲的作用：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H2> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、能帮助作者和指导老师明确写作的总体思路。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">使学生掌握全篇论文的基本骨架，使论文的结构完整统一。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、能帮助学生明确各部分之间的逻辑联系。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分清层次，确定重点，周密地谋篇布局，使总论点和分论点有机地统一起来，有利于避免各部分之间互相矛盾。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、能帮助学生合理利用资料。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）学生可以根据提纲，按照各部分的要求安排、组织资料，决定取舍。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">有的学生写论文的时候，不管资料是否可用，反正全部塞进去再说，这样既浪费自己很多写作的时间，也浪<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"费指导\">费指导</st1:PersonName>老师阅读的时间。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）通过编写提纲，学生可以看出哪些资料是与自己的观点一致的，哪些资料是与自己的观点相反的。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">与自己的观点一致的资料，可以用来论证自己的观点；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">与自己的观点相反的资料，自己要思考怎样反驳，这些资料的错误和不足在哪里？</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">◆有些学生不大愿意写提纲，喜欢直接写初稿。如果不是在头脑中已把全文的提纲想好，如果心中对于全文的论点、论据和论证步骤还是混乱的，那么编写一个提纲是十分必要的。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、有利于及时调整，避免大返工。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">首先，便于指导。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">初写论文的学生，如果把自己的思路先写成提纲，再去请教他人，人家一看能懂，较易提出一些修改补充的意见，便于自己得到有效的指导。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">其次，有利于学生驾御自己的思路。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">在毕业论文的研究和写作过程中，作者的思维活动是非常活跃的，一些不起眼的材料，从表面看来不相关的材料，经过熟悉和深思，常常会产生新的联想或新的观点，如果不认真编写提纲，动起笔来就会被这种现象所干扰，不得不停下笔来重新思考，甚至推翻已写的从头来过。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <H1 style=\"MARGIN: 17pt 0cm 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二、提纲基本结构</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 22.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H1> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">论题（论文的总题目）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">总论点</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">(</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">上位论点</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">(</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">)(</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">下位论点</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times 