农村留守儿童等）、帮孤助残、支教扫盲、青少年援助、环境保护、交通规则宣传、疾病预防宣传等公益性活动，推动青年志愿者协会体系的建立和完善。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第八条：为本系发展、学校建设、扶贫开发、抢险救灾、社会公益以及大型庆典活动等提供志愿服务。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第九条：为具有特殊困难以及需要帮助的广在教职工和在校学生其他社会成员提供服务。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第十条：维护和代表青年志愿者的合法权益，致力于推进志愿者行动的规范化建设，为志愿者行动创造良好的外部环境。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第十一条：组织、策划各个时期全系青年志愿服务活动，协调、指导本系部青年志愿者组织开展工作，定期向学校各部门通报志愿者活动情况，争取媒体支持做好志愿者活动的宣传工作。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第十二条：开展与外系部青年志愿者组织的团体交流。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">第十三条：向全系公开招募志愿者，培养青年志愿者及青年志愿者组织的管理者，建立一批由本组织管理的专项青年志愿者服务队伍，更好的开展志愿者服务行动。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: -42.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: list 42.75pt\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: -42.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: list 