yle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\">三、证明材料：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\">被保险人若有理赔发生，将理赔资料汇总后，由服务县项目办出具事故经过证明并盖章后，附上被保险人联系电话、指定的银行账号、开户银行的详细名称）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体\">四：寄送地址：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋\">北京市西城区金融街<SPAN lang=EN-US>23</SPAN>号平安大厦九层<SPAN lang=EN-US>915</SPAN>室，宋庆锋收，邮编：<SPAN lang=EN-US>100032<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></DIV>', '学生工作', '工作安排', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-04-17 00:00:00', '433', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('219', '衡阳师范学院人文社会科学系开展深入学习实践科学发展观', '<DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">衡阳师范学院人文社会科学系开展深入学习实践科学发展观</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">活动学习调研阶段工作方案</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">学习调研阶段是深入学习实践科学发展观活动工作的重要环节，是搞好分析检查、整改落实阶段的工作基础和前提。现根据学院党委学习实践科学发展观活动工作实施意见，制定人文社会科学系学习调研阶段工作方案：</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">一、时间安排</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>3</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">月中旬</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">—6</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">月下旬</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">二、基本要求</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">这一阶段主要围绕解放思想进行学习讨论，主要任务是学好理论，提高认识，统一思想，转变观念。系党政领导班子和广大党员要对照要求，联系实际，创新方法，带头认真学习科学发展观，准确把握科学发展观的重大意义、科学内涵、精神实质和根本要求，切实增强贯彻落实科学发展观的自觉性和坚定性；要在把握理论精髓的基础上，深入师生员工中间，带头开展专题调研，梳理调研问题，形成调研报告；要围绕实践载体开展大讨论大交流，进一步解放思想，转变观念，凝聚共识。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"> </SPAN></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">三、学习内容</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">（一）党的十七大和十七届三中全会精神；</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">（二）《毛泽东邓小平江泽民胡锦涛论科学发展》；</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">（三）《科学发展观重要论述摘编》；</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">四、方法步骤</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">（一）宣传发动，全面部署</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">借助系部网页、板报等宣传载体，通报前期筹备和本阶段各项工作，营造良好氛围。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">在</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">4</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">月初召开全系动员大会。包括全系在职教职工党员、学生党员。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">动员大会后，成立本单位学习实践活动小组，讨论制定学习实践活动方案与学习调研阶段工作安排，学习实践活动方案要求简洁明了，可操作性强，工作安排以表格形式上报。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">（二）</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"> </SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">分类指导，加强学习</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">联系实际，根据学习实践活动指定材料，积极创新学习形式，除集中学习培训外，可采取自学的方式，认真研读指定学习材料，做好学习笔记，写好学习心得；并通过学习指导调研，在调研中深化学习，在学习调研基础上，组织全系党员广泛开展大讨论大交流，进一步解放思想，转变观念，提升学习效果。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">（三）联系实际，深入调研</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">广大党员要紧密联系实际，在认真学习理论的基础上，按照高起点梳理调研思路、高质量确立调研题目、高要求抓好调研过程、高水平撰写调研报告等要求认真做好调研工作。调研活动应在活动开始就进行，并于</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">5</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">月中旬前完成。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">调研工作的主要任务是配合做好学院的专题调研工作，同时结合本系实际，对照科学发展的要求，深入调研并提出本系拟解决的若干个突出问题，以及相应的思路、举措和意见建议。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">（四）组织讨论，凝聚共识</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">集中讨论在</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">4</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">月中旬</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">-</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">下旬进行。组织全系党员分层次学习、专题研讨、交流会，围绕</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">“</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">科学发展，质量兴校</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">”</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">，广泛开展大讨论大交流，进一步解放思想，努力在思想解放中统一思想，在促进我系科学发展的理念、思路、机制、举措方面形成共识，打牢我系科学发展的坚实的思想基础。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"></SPAN></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 衡阳师范学院人文社会科学系</SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"></SPAN></B><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" />