 mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">另：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、本学期科研部、宣传部都将开展常规活动：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 90pt; TEXT-INDENT: -90pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -7.5\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">科研部：每月一次“学术交流</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">活动；并不定期地开展科研兴趣小组讨论；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 102pt; TEXT-INDENT: -102pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -8.5\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">宣传部：开办“时政宣传栏”对每周时政大事进行盘点、展出、宣传，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 102pt; TEXT-INDENT: -102pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -8.5\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">并征集时政论文进行评比。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 102pt; TEXT-INDENT: -102pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -8.5\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、社会实践部及长春花志愿者协会将根据实际情况适时地组织本系学生参</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 101.9pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -5.0; mso-para-margin-left: 3.99gd\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">与社会实践活动。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 101.9pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-char-indent-count: -5.0; mso-para-margin-left: 3.99gd\" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 101.9pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-char-indent-count: -5.0; mso-para-margin-left: 3.99gd\" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 101.9pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-char-indent-count: -5.0; mso-para-margin-left: 3.99gd\" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人文系办公室</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 101.9pt; TEXT-INDENT: -60pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-char-indent-count: -5.0; mso-para-margin-left: 3.99gd\" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P></DIV>', '学生工作', '计划总结', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-06 00:00:00', '237', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('224', '“反藏独，反歪曲报道，支持奥运，爱我中华。”宣传活动', '<DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">在<SPAN lang=EN-US>2008</SPAN>年北京奥运会即将开幕之际，举国上下为奥运摇旗呐喊之时，不和谐的声音传来了。“<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" TCSC=\"0\" NumberType=\"1\" Negative=\"False\" HasSpace=\"False\" SourceValue=\"3.14\" UnitName=\"”\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>3.14</SPAN>”</st1:chmetcnv>西藏暴乱划破的不仅仅是那片圣土的宁静，也激起了国内外一片喧哗。国内“藏独”分子活动频繁，国外一些媒体对华坚持不实报道，对中国人民的感情造成了严重伤害。此时，中国人民决不沉默。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">我系<SPAN lang=EN-US>07</SPAN>级政教班因着专业敏感性及强烈的爱国精神，经院、系领导批准，策划并组织了“反藏独，反歪曲报道，支持奥运，爱我中华。”大型宣传活动。以“五四”青年节为契机，面向全院同学展开了一次爱国思想教育活动。不仅旨在揭露达赖集团的藏独行径与西方媒体歪曲报道的险恶用心，宣传国人的爱国活动，更是为了彰显我院学生与民族共荣辱的感情与信念，并提倡“理性爱国”。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">此次活动得到了系团总支学生分会及系领导的大力支持，由我系<SPAN lang=EN-US>07</SPAN>级政教班全体同学齐力完成，一共制作了三块板报，其内容分别为“达赖的生平事迹及叛国行为”、“西方歪曲报道的事实”、“国人的爱国事实”。板报连同内容为“反藏独，反歪曲报道，支持奥运，爱我中华。”的横幅于<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"28\" Month=\"4\" Year=\"2008\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>28</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>与<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"29\" Month=\"4\" Year=\"2008\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>29</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>在新校区虹桥展出。这期间，板报前阅读的同学一直络绎不绝。而此次活动在吸引了全院同学注意力，唤起其爱国热情的同时，又宣传了“理性爱国”的思想，在“五四”到来之际，让师生感受作日历史，让我们不忘青年的责任。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><?xml:namespace prefix = v ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" /><v:shapetype id=_x0000_t136 path=\"m@7,l@8,m@5,21600l@6,21600e\" adj=\"10800\" o:spt=\"136\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\"><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"sum #0 0 10800\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod #0 2 1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 21600 0 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 21600 0 @3\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"if @0 @3 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"if @0 21600 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"if @0 0 @2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"if @0 @4 21600\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"mid @5 @6\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"mid @8 @5\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"mid @7 @8\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"mid @6 @7\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @6 0 @5\"></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:connectangles=\"270,180,90,0\" o:connectlocs=\"@9,0;@10,10800;@11,21600;@12,10800\" o:connecttype=\"custom\" textpathok=\"t\"></v:path><v:textpath fitshape=\"t\" on=\"t\"></v:textpath><v:handles><v:h xrange=\"6629,14971\" position=\"#0,bottomRight\"></v:h></v:handles><o:lock shapetype=\"t\" text=\"t\" v:ext=\"edit\"></o:lock></v:shapetype><v:shape id=_x0000_s1027 style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 306.4pt; Z-INDEX: -1; LEFT: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 198pt; WIDTH: 239.25pt; POSITION: absolute; HEIGHT: 18.75pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left\" type=\"#_x0000_t136\" strokecolor=\"#909\"><v:shadow color=\"#868686\"></v:shadow><v:textpath style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'华文行楷\'; v-text-align: right; v-text-kern: t\" string=\"＿＿人文社科系＿2008年＿＿\" fitpath=\"t\" trim=\"t\"></v:textpath></v:shape><v:shape id=_x0000_s1026 style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 283pt; Z-INDEX: -2; LEFT: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 198pt; WIDTH: 239.25pt; POSITION: absolute; HEIGHT: 18.75pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left\" type=\"#_x0000_t136\" strokecolor=\"#909\"><v:shadow color=\"#868686\"></v:shadow><v:textpath style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'华文行楷\'; v-text-align: right; v-text-kern: t\" string=\"＿＿人文社科系＿2008年＿＿\" fitpath=\"t\" trim=\"t\"></v:textpath></v:shape><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">另外，此次活动的一大特色便是，活动由<SPAN lang=EN-US>07</SPAN>级政教班以班为单位策划、组织，系团总支学生分会协助而面向全院师生，不仅体现了我系敢于创新的精神，也表现了我系学生分会与各班级之间的充分信任及融洽的合作关系。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '学生工作', '班级风采', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '326', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('225', '人文社会科学生08级新生内务评比', '<DIV> <DIV> <BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style=\"MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px\"> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">秉承“德育为首、教学为主、育人为本<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN>的教育理念，遵循“自我教育、自我管理、自我服务”的“三自”原则，积极推动素质教育的发展，人文系开展了<SPAN lang=EN-US>08</SPAN>级新生的内务评比活动。在系领导的正确领导下，在各部门的有力配合下，在全体新生的积极参与下，本次活动取得了不错的成绩。同学们都用心经营爱护着自己的宿舍，都是严格按照军训要求来执行，天花板洁白无尘、门窗干净、玻璃透明、书桌摆放整齐、被褥毛毯棱角分明、生活用品排成一直线等等，营造出了温馨的宿舍文化氛围。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">此次活动按照军训期间的严格要求，在宿管部成员的指导下，由寝室长统一安排，同学们认真保护宿舍的文明卫生，注重培养良好的生活习惯，宿舍里面也是整洁明亮。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">在评比期间，宿管部进行卫生的总结，发现问题及时解决，并且对各个宿舍进行小评，发扬优秀的，指正落后的，形成一种互相追赶的局面，创造良好的宿舍。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">通过这次的活动，同学们的集体荣誉感和凝聚力不断的增强，团结协作、互助互利的精神也得到进一步的发扬。同时，这一系列的活动体现了“厚德、博学、励志、笃行”的师院精神，突显了师院的人文关怀色彩，更展现了人文系的风采。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">按照“公平、公正、公开”的原则，大一新生内务的评比结果如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></BLOCKQUOTE> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style=\"MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px\"> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">男生优秀宿舍：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" TCSC=\"0\" NumberType=\"1\" Negative=\"False\" HasSpace=\"False\" SourceValue=\"4\" UnitName=\"a\">4A</st1:chmetcnv>-104<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">女生优秀宿舍：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">一等宿舍：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" TCSC=\"0\" NumberType=\"1\" Negative=\"False\" HasSpace=\"False\" SourceValue=\"7\" UnitName=\"a\">7A</st1:chmetcnv>-211<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">二等宿舍：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" TCSC=\"0\" NumberType=\"1\" Negative=\"False\" HasSpace=\"False\" SourceValue=\"7\" UnitName=\"a\">7A</st1:chmetcnv>-110<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\">三等宿舍：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" TCSC=\"0\" NumberType=\"1\" Negative=\"False\" HasSpace=\"False\" SourceValue=\"7\" UnitName=\"a\">7A</st1:chmetcnv>-108<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></BLOCKQUOTE> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 28pt 0pt 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 28pt 0pt 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></B></P></DIV></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '346', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('226', '我系举行趣味知识抢答赛', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为了丰富同学们的校园文化生活，提高同学们的学习兴趣，增强大学生活的趣味性，学习部组织了一次趣味知识竞答赛。本次大赛参赛人员由大一、大二、大三各班的同学组成，共六个班，每班一个代表队，每队三人。经过精心准备，活动于<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"3\" Month=\"12\" Year=\"2008\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>周三晚<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>点在文综楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>301</SPAN>准时开始。同学们的热情很高，除<SPAN lang=EN-US>06</SPAN>级政教班因特殊原因未能到场做弃权处理外，其余个班代表队都准时到场，为配合比赛流程，我们从观众中抽取了一个临时代表队参赛。整个比赛按预定程序进行，选手们积极思考认真答题，并获得了比较优秀的成绩。比赛结束后，根据各队得分情况评出了一、二、三等奖各一名，如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一等奖：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>07</SPAN>历史<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二等奖：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>07</SPAN>政教<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">三等奖：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>08</SPAN>政教<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P>&nbsp;</P></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '326', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('227', '人文系第五届“人文杯”篮球赛顺利举行', '<DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=宋体>运动是生活的主旋律，伴随着我们成长。系篮球，这道丰富的大餐，不仅给了我们视觉上的享受，而且让我们心灵受到了震撼。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P> <P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">伴随着海浪般的欢呼声，第五届“人文杯”篮球赛已于</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\">2009年3月10日到19日在东校区体育馆前篮球场举行。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P> <P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">由于系领导及学生会的支持，各部门的积极配合，特别是宣传部的全程拍摄及篮球海报的制作，以及同学们的踊跃参与，此次比赛取得丰硕果实。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: purple; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 黑体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">在此次比赛中，大三球队的精湛球技、自我风格的战术大大增加了球赛的观赏性，大二球队的顽强拼搏、坚持不懈把人文精神表现的淋漓尽致，新生犹如初生牛犊让我们看到了我系强大的后备军。秉承“比赛第一，友谊第二”精神的球赛，不仅给我们提供了一场视觉盛宴，而且加强了班级之间的联系、增进了同学们之间的交流、提高了班级凝聚力。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">经过激烈的角逐，比赛结果如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">冠军：男子组：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">06</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">历史</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">女子组：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">07</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">政教</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">亚军：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>08</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">历史</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</SPAN>06</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">政教</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">季军：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>06</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">政教</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>08</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">政教</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 301pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 21.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV></DIV></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '167', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('228', '人文系首届封面设计比赛圆满落幕', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">随着社会日新月异的发展，“包装”也越来越流行，好的包装更能吸引人们的眼球，这是社会给人们带来的提示。作为师范生的我们，都希望将来能出版一本属于自己的书，一本具有独特魅力的书，因此封面的设计将是对我们的一大挑战。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">因此，我系于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">09</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">年</SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"11\" Month=\"3\" Year=\"2009\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">——</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">23</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日举行了人文系首届封面设计大赛。此次比赛主要针对我系</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">06</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">07</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">08</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">级学生，同学们报名踊跃，参与热情高涨。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">经过系宣传部评委评选，此次比赛的获奖名单如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一等奖：赵清</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二等奖：吴晓婵、刘梦尧</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">三等奖：颜娟娟、王汪、罗校</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">优胜奖：杨柳、肖露珊、尹望凤、周玲、赖蓉</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '206', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('229', '人文系第五届干部培训', '<DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">为了培养我系干部的领导能力和凝聚力<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>提高系干的工作素质<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>同时<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>为了处理好系内的各种问题<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>加快系内各方面的工作效率<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>我部门于第六周周二举行了人文系第五届干部培训。此次干部培训的实质效果在于让系内每一个干部明确<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>做人<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>在工作中的重要位置<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>认识到培养自己的素质<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>特别是自己的领导能力和凝聚力的具体做法<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>学会换角度<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>换位置看问题和思考问题。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">本次干部培训的主讲老师邓书记主要从以下四个方面为我们讲述了如何做一个好干部<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>以及一个好干部所应该具备的最基本的素质和能力<SPAN lang=EN-US>:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">一<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>学会做人<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">做人<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>尤其做好人是做好一个干部的出发点<SPAN lang=EN-US>,\"</SPAN>低调做人<SPAN lang=EN-US>\"</SPAN>是做人的核心和关键所在。首先，它表现为宽宏大量地对待身边的人，此所谓<SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN>海纳百川，有容乃大<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN>；第二，<SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN>为人正直<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN>是做一个好人的重要衡量尺度，也是身为一个干部的凝聚力所在；再次，<SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN>学会善解人意<SPAN lang=EN-US>’</SPAN>，也就是说换位思考，是处理矛盾和问题的有效途径。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">二<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>要培养自己的素质，提高自己的能力。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">学会做人的同时，每一个干部都应在同学之间树立自己的权威，也就是说每一个干部都应多学习，广泛的学习，<SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN>三人行，必有我师焉<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN>，同时，注意自己的言行仪表，养成良好的习惯，也是每一个干部给他人留下深刻印象的重要方式。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">三<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>培养自己的领导能力和凝聚力<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">身为干部，最主要的，也是最突出的一点，便是领导能力和凝聚力的高低。一个没有领导能力和凝聚力的干部，注定不能成为一个好的干部，也不能带动和号召其他的同学。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">四<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN>学会处理矛盾和问题<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">塞翁失马，焉知祸福<SPAN lang=EN-US>”“</SPAN>福兮祸兮<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN>，换一个角度看问题，换一个位置思考问题，能够有效的解决各种问题和矛盾，特别是同学之间的矛盾。因此，超出问题的本身，回到问题的效果，能够更好地处理各种矛盾和问题。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">在干部培训的最后，每个部门都就本部门遇到的突出问题，征求了其他个部门的意见和建议，在一定程度上有助于各部门问题的有效解决。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">本次干部培训的召开，在一定程度上影响了各干部的工作素质，培养了干部工作的自觉意识，希望各部门干部在以后的工作中能够朝着专业化，有效化的方向发展。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '208', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('230', '人文系师范素质五项技能大赛活动', '<DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">根据《关于举办衡阳师范学院大学生师范素质五项技能大赛活动的通知》的相关要求，人文系</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">学习部在第<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>周至第<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>周</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">组织举办了“师范素质五项技能”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">大赛。本次大赛面向全系同学开展<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>旨在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">引导“准教师”们树立“拓展素质、献身教育”的理念<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">为以后走向教师这个岗位积累经验<SPAN lang=EN-US>,</SPAN>同时给所有同学提供一个模拟教学平台和学习交流的机会。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">本次大赛内容包括授课、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">粉笔字</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">、现场答问和才艺表演四个方面。通过这些主要考察同学们的课堂教学能力、现场应变能力及才艺素质。课堂教学能力主要考察选手的普通话、板书、粉笔字以及选手的专业知识和综合形象；现场应变能力主要考察选手的处理师生关系、管理班级及教学过程中出现的突发问题的能力；才艺表演则考察选手才艺素质的发展。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">大赛分为初赛、复赛和决赛三个阶段。由于大家的参赛积极性非常高，报名人数占到全系人数的三分之二，但考虑到评委、场地和时间有限，本部门经讨论决定对参赛的人员做了一定的限制：大一、大二每班选三名同学参加初赛，对大三、大四同学不作人数限制。但这并没有削减大一、大二同学的热情，他们的选手都是通过本班进行比赛而推选上来的。从整体而言，三个阶段的比赛进行得都比较顺利，达到了比赛的预期效果。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">经过三轮的激烈角逐，根据评委的评分我们评出了所有的奖项，具体情况如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">特等奖：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-tab-count: 1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">邓婷</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一等奖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">:&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-tab-count: 2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">陈丽</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二等奖：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-tab-count: 1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">任杰、宋思思</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">三等奖：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-tab-count: 1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">邝文娟、汤江南、罗艳</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">优胜奖：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-tab-count: 1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">黄红娟、孙静、陈洁、王诗雨</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;<FONT size=1><A href=\"http://songfeiok.wsu.wsu.cn/bbs/index.asp\">宝庆论坛</A></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV></DIV></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '319', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('231', '2009年上学期人文系第一次理论交流会', '<DIV><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">金融危机余寒未消，世界经济局势扑朔迷离，为了解决金融危机所带来的各种隐患，四月五日，包括中国在内在世界范围内举足轻重的二十个国家的元首齐聚伦敦，共商解除危机隐患，以拯救陷入泥潭的世界经济的决策。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">从“<SPAN lang=EN-US>G20</SPAN>峰会大国之间的角逐与妥协”出发，我系理论小组成员在系组织部的策划下，于<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2009\" Month=\"4\" Day=\"15\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>在文综楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>204</SPAN>举行了本学期第一次理论学习小组的讨论活动。活动现场气氛活跃，成员们从不同角度展开思索与讨论，各抒己见。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">此次活动紧跟时事，从身边的实际出发，给每位成员提供了一个交流思想与展现自我的平台，充分体现了我系理论学习小组的活动特色。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></SPAN></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '298', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('232', '人文系第二届粉笔字比赛', '<DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.05pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">为提高我系学生专业素质，培养同学们作为师范生的技能，丰富大家的兴趣爱好，我系于本学期</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">第四周星期三晚<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>点至<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>点在文综楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>301</SPAN>举行了针对<SPAN lang=EN-US>06</SPAN>级、<SPAN lang=EN-US>07</SPAN>级、<SPAN lang=EN-US>08</SPAN>级同学的系第二届粉笔字比赛。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.05pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">此次比赛历时之久，从提议到策划经过了两周的精心部署。规模之大，大一、大二同学积极踊跃参与到此次比赛，大三同学更是忙里抽闲参与其中。参赛选手共达<SPAN lang=EN-US>65</SPAN>人。影响之深，无论在赛前或是赛后均激起了同学们练好粉笔字的兴趣以及写好粉笔字的决心。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.05pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">我系举办的粉笔字比赛为同学们提供了“学习”、“交流”的平台，同学们可以在这个属于自己的舞台上充分发挥自己的才智，展示自我风采，在切磋技能的过程中相互学习，共同提高。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.05pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">本次比赛旨在培养同学们兴趣的基础上更进一步拓展学生的才能。它的成功举办给予了我们更大的信心和兴趣更好的做好今后有如此类的比赛。<FONT color=#ffffff><A href=\"http://songfeiok.wsu.wsu.cn/\"><FONT size=1 color=#ffffff>邵阳广告招贴</FONT></A><FONT size=1>网</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-07 00:00:00', '414', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('233', '人文社会科学系党总支召开学习实践科学发展观座谈会', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"12\" Month=\"5\" Year=\"2009\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">12</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">和</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">13</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">日，人文社会科学系党总支为深入学习实践科学发展观，创建和谐系部，将服务师生的宗旨落到实处，分别召开了由教师代表和学生代表参加的座谈会。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 33.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.4; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">在座谈会中，系党总支书记邓长飞同志首先就学院、系部学习实践科学发展观的开展情况向与会代表做了介绍，鼓励大家广开言路，找出找准问题，为学院和系部的发展献计献策。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">与会党员、教师代表主要围绕如何促进我系又好又快发展、如何加快我系学科建设以及教师如何转型以适应我系发展要求等议题展开了热烈的讨论。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\"> <BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">科学发展观的第一要义是发展，发展是硬道理。我系现所开专业，机遇与挑战并存，如何结合学校整体发展规划以及经济社会发展的需要把我系发展壮大，这是摆在我系全体教师面前一个务实而艰巨的任务。与会老师认为，要把学科建设专业建设作为我系今后建设的重点来抓，通过学科专业建设来提升我系的核心竞争力和提高办学效益，争取培育若干个有特色的学科和专业。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">关于我系教师如何转型以适应我系新专业的发展要求的问题，我系未来将增设部分新专业，在未来新专业的师资问题上除了通过各种方式引进人才以外，我系老师还要结合自己的专业特长开设部分专业主干课程，因此，各位老师要做好各种准备，积极主动学习新知识，思考今后个人发展方向和进修计划，以适应我系今后发展的需要。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 33.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.4; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">学生代表在座谈会中就就业等方面提了相关的问题，并且从学生角度出发，围绕如何更好的服务学生开展了深入的讨论，如学生党员代表就提出了在学生公寓成立并有效利用党员活动室为学生提供帮助等建议。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">最后，邓书记对座谈会进行了总结，他代表总支感谢大家积极参加并提出宝贵意见；同时表示对于大家反映的问题，在系部能力范围内的一定抓紧落实，系部能力范围以外的将尽快的如实反映给学院党委和相关的职能部门，争取早日将科学发展做实事落到实处。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 98pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 7.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 182pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 13.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">衡阳师范学院人文社会科学系党总支</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 238pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 17.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"14\" Month=\"5\" Year=\"2009\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\">2009</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\">14</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV>', '近期工作', '本站通知', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-14 00:00:00', '289', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('234', '人文社会科学系召开学习实践科学发展观专题民主生活会', '<DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 36.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.45; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"25\" Month=\"5\" Year=\"2009\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>25</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">下午，按照院学习实践活动领导小组的部署，人文社会科学系党总支召开专题民主生活会。人文社会科学系党总支成员邓长飞、廖建平、伍辉、魏文生、谢华等参加会议，并邀请民主党派代表唐林生副主任、教师党员代表喻冰峰、刘余香和非党员教师代表王卫国等列席。院党委组织部部长聂东明同志到会指导。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>会上，人文社会科学系党总支书记邓长飞同志首先介绍了前一段调研情况，并谈到</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">为了开好这次的民主生活会，人文社会科学系党总支作了大量的前期准备工作。召开了二个座谈会，一是教工座谈会，二是学生座谈会。在二个座谈会中，党总支充分听取了教师与学生的发言和建议，并举行了第二次问卷调查活动，这次问卷调查的主要内容，主要是围绕人文系领导班子在教学、管理和对教职工的人文关怀等方面征求教师们的意见，同时还着重征求教师们对领导班子个人在党性党风党纪等方面的意见。还开展了班子成员相互之间的谈心交心活动，系党总支书记与系主任都分别与两位副主任开展了谈心交心活动。系党总支把开展的这些活动所搜集的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">意见和建议<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>条，涉及<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>个方面</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">，原汁原味的集中起来，分别送到每一个班子成员手中，并要求班子成员根据这些建议和意见撰写民主生活会的发言稿。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">班子成员根据师生员工提出的意见和建议，认真查找个人和班子成员在贯彻落实科学发展观方面存在的突出问题，查找个人在党性党风党纪方面存在的问题，并深刻剖析其主观原因，开展批评和自我批评。大家坦诚相对、开诚布公、畅所欲言，整个专题民主生活会始终弥漫着团结、民主、和谐的氛围。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 37.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">最后，院党委组织部部长聂东明同志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">对人文社会科学系专题民主生活会给予了高度肯定，认为准备充分，开得认真，剖析透彻，是一个高质量的民主生活会，并指出人文社会科学系的班子是一个廉洁奉公、团结和谐、求真务实的领导班子。同时也要求人文系班子围绕“发展”查找问题，寻找解决问题的方案。人文社会科学系下一步的发展，需要进一步解放思想，突破目前制约发展的危局，关键是要整合现有资源，形成团队优势。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">他要求人文社会科学系党总支要发挥核心作用，进行广泛的调研，认真的研究，写出一份高质量的调研报告。（人文社会科学系供稿）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '近期工作', '本站通知', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-26 00:00:00', '697', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('235', '我系成功举办“找工作经验交流会”', '<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.85pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"20\" Month=\"5\" Year=\"2009\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">&nbsp;作为我系每年的特色学习活动，“找工作经验交流会”都会在每年的大四的同学即将离校时举办。此活动旨在向低年级同学透露就业的相关动态信息，让同学们了解自身应该从哪些方面加强学习与锻炼，使自己在找工作方面具有更强的竞争力。</SPAN></st1:chsdate></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.85pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"20\" Month=\"5\" Year=\"2009\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">&nbsp;5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">晚</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">7</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">00</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">，学习部在文综楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">301</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">举办了“找工作经验交流会”。交流会请到了即将05即的学长学姐为低年级学生讲述自己找工作的亲身经历，并且与大家分享自己的经验，给予自己的建议。交流会现场人气高涨，气氛热烈，同学们对学长学姐们积极提出自己内心的疑惑，05级的同学们也知无不言，言无不尽，使得到会同学都获益匪浅。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2009-05-30 00:00:00', '275', '0');
