bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></SPAN></st1:chsdate> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"11\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"11\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><IMG height=319 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/4314112010144224_3.gif\" width=559 align=middle border=1></SPAN></st1:chsdate></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"11\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">首席专家廖建平教授正在与学员们交流</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"11\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" Year=\"2010\" Month=\"11\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">上午，副院长张登玉教授来到文科楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>622</SPAN>教室，对<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>年初中思想品德“国培”置换班培训工作进行了全面调研。陪同调研的还有继续教育学院院长涂昊教授、培训科科长蒋</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">瀚洋。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">副院长张登玉首先兴致勃勃地和学员们一起听课，仔细查看了他们的课堂笔记，随后抽取了部分学员代表进行座谈。思想品德课程教师培训学科首席专家、人文社会科学系主<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"任廖建平\">任廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授、党总支书记廖新<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"平副\">平副</st1:PersonName>教授等参加了座谈会。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">座谈会上，学员们畅所欲言，讲述了自参训以来的感想和收获，并提出了一些很好的建议。<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"廖建平\">廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授就培训工作进展情况向张副院长进行了简要汇报。他说，人文系高度重视本次培训工作，精心拟定培训方案，科学安排教学内容，确保学员真正学有所获。在课堂内容安排上，遵循从理论到实际的原则，连贯自然，层层推进，先是给学员讲述现代教育、素质教育、思想品德新课改等最新教育思想，进而过渡到对课堂教学艺术的把握，最后让每个学员进行实战演习，结合所学知识至少讲一堂公开课，真正做到学以致用。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">在听取了工作汇报和代表发言后，张副院长首先对我系在本次培训中的策划组织、授课专家的精心挑选以及对学员学习和生活的周到安排等工作给予了充分肯定，对学员们认真学习的态度给予了高度赞扬，然后对我们以后的培训工作提出了下列要求：一是在培训后期要组织学员进行示范教学，所有的学员都要参加评课，通过这样的活动切实提高受训教师的教学能力；二是学员们在撰写论文时一定要结合本校的实际和本人的真实感受，真正体现本次培训的学习成果；三是组织者要为学员们多组织一些文化、体育活动，丰富他们的业余生活。不仅让学员们学有所得、学有所成，还要让他们在衡阳师范学院生活愉快。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">最后，涂昊教授针对一些学员提出的问题作了解答，并鼓励各位受训教师要从自身做起、从本班本校做起，将所学的新思想、新观念贯彻到实际工作中去，努力改变农村基础教育的落后局面。（人文系供稿）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', '近期工作', null, '3', '4314112010144224_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-04 00:00:00', '158', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('272', '“国培计划——湖南省初中思想品德课骨干教师短期集中培训班”在我院开班', '<DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><IMG height=336 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/97911112010104923_1.gif\" width=502 align=center border=1></SPAN></st1:chsdate></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">开班典礼现场</SPAN></st1:chsdate></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><IMG height=533 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/97911112010104923_2.gif\" width=502 align=middle border=1></SPAN></st1:chsdate></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">副院长张登玉教授出席开班典礼并讲话</SPAN></st1:chsdate></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"10\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">上午，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">2010</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">年衡阳师范学院“国培计划——湖南省初中思想品德课教师培训项目”——初中思想品德骨干教师短期集中培训班开班典礼在衡阳市委党校培训部举行。出席典礼的嘉宾有学院副院长张登玉教授、继续教育学院副院长卜华白博士、思想品德课程教师培训学科首席专家、人文社会科学系系主任廖建平教授、人文系党总支书记廖新平副教授、培训班联络员凌云志老师、班导师谢芳和李斯老师以及相关培训学科负责人。典礼由廖新平书记主持。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\"></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">副院长张登玉教授首先代表学院致欢迎辞，向全省各地的思想品德课的教师表示热烈的欢迎和衷心的祝福，并真诚期待各位同仁对本次培训工作以及衡阳师范学院的建设和发展多提宝贵意见。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">张副院长说，近年来学院先后成功多个中小学校长和学科培训班，逐步积累了培训经验，充实了培训师资，优化了培训条件，提升了培训水平。多年来，人文社会科学系重视教师教育，注重师资队伍的培训工作，对中学教学和教研有比较全面的了解，完成或参与了多次的衡阳市中学教师培训工作。从</SPAN><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"17\" Month=\"10\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">17</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">开始，人文社会科学系在衡阳师范学院新校区主办为期三个月的国培计划——初中思想品德课教师置换培训班，为本次培训积累了丰富的经验。张院长表示，学院将秉承高度负责的态度，遴选优秀师资，投入一流的设施，配备专业精干的工作队伍，满怀热情做好培训和服务工作，为专家和学员营造良好的教学环境、舒适的生活环境、和愉快的交流环境。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">继续教育学院副院长<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"卜华白\">卜华白</st1:PersonName>博士从本院的立校之本以及国家发展战略等各个角度就本次培训的意义作了讲话。他说，衡阳师院百年师范传统，教师教育特色，使得我们必须把对基础教育教师培训作为我们的一项事业。加强教师培训工作，也是落实科学发展观，促进教育公平，提高教育质量的重要举措。并且，教师专业成长的内在需求呼唤更加有效的支持性平台。他说，“未来不仅仅是我们想去的地方，更是我们要创造的地方，未来的路不是找到的，而一步一个脚印脚踏实地走出来的。”他勉励所有受训教师树大志，干大事，成大师。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">培训学科首席专<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"家廖建平\">家廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授就本次培训工作做了详细的说明。<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"廖建平\">廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授首先希望各位学员充分认识培训的重要性，他说，首先，培训是真正落实终身教育的一种有效形式；是补充新思想、新理念、新知识的需要；是建设学习型社会的需要。同时，<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"廖\">廖</st1:PersonName>教授还向受训学员提出了明确的学习任务和相关的纪律要求。他祝愿各位受训教师在衡阳师院身体健康、生活愉快并真正学有所获。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">来自郴州的<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"田世辉\">田世辉</st1:PersonName>老师代表培训班学员作了发言。典礼最后，所有嘉宾与全体培训学员一起合影留念。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">本次培训是由国家教育部、财政部支持的国培计划——</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">2010</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">年湖南省初中思想品德骨干教师短期集中培训班，来自全省各地区的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">160</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\">名从事基础思想品德课教育的一线教师参加，目的在于有效提升各位参训教师的综合素质，发挥大家在初中思想品德课的教学中的引领示范作用，切实增强初中学生的德育效果，推动我省初中思想品德课程的教学和研究迈上一个新的台阶。（人文社会科学系凌云志供稿）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '近期工作', null, '2', '97911112010104923_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-10 00:00:00', '158', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('273', '华南师范大学邝丽湛教授应邀为国培班学员作专题学术讲座', '<DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=395 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/12018112010184418_1.gif\" width=554 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center><FONT face=宋体>邝丽湛教授在给学员做报告</FONT></DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"2\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"2\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">，华南师范大学硕士生导师邝丽湛教授应邀来我院思想品德课国培置换培训班讲学，在文科楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">622</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">多媒体教室举行了一场题为“思想品德课程标准（修订版）解读”的学术讲座，讲座由人文社会科学系伍辉副主任主持。人文社会科学系</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">多名教师和所有国培班学员聆听了讲座。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">讲座中，邝教授首先介绍了思想品德课程标准修订概况，她认为新课标的修订在突出思想品德课程特点的前提下，紧跟时代发展的步伐，体现以人为本，合理增加科学发展观、核心价值观、公民教育三部分教育内容，注意培养生态文明意识和确立全球化视野，强调情感发展对品德培养的重要性。随后，邝教授重点向学员们介绍了新课标具体的修订内容与根据，她特别强调教学和评价部分是此次修订的重点，指出这部分修改的具体的思路是：①坚持课程改革的方向、理念和要求，推动思想品德课程改革向前发展，而不是后退。在教学建议和评价建议部分，增加了简单明了的指导语，确立了教学工作和评价工作的基本立场和方向。此外，十分强调思想品德教学要与生活相联系；十分强调学生学习方式的变革；十分强调教学与评价过程中正确的价值引领。②在坚持改革的同时，又注重处理好一些关系，比如道德知识学习与道德践行的关系，接受性学习与探究性学习的关系，提出要加强道德、心理健康、法律及国情等内容的整合，以指导教师在坚持改革的同时，辩证地处理问题。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">在一个上午的讲座中，邝丽<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"湛\">湛</st1:PersonName>教授不仅介绍了最新的思想品德课改革的情况，同时注重联系中学教学实际，并针对一些具体的问题与听课学员作了交流。讲座最后，伍辉副主任代表人文系对邝教授前来讲学表示感谢。学员<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"和\">和</st1:PersonName>老师们听完讲座后纷纷表示，邝教授的讲座为我们带来了新的理念，让大家开阔了视野，启迪了思维，很有收获。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 10.6pt 0pt 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 23.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; tab-stops: 27.0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">邝丽<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"湛\">湛</st1:PersonName>教授简介：</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">华南师范大学硕士生导师、教授、教育硕士（政治）导师组组长；广东省基础教育课程教学指导委员会委员，《思想品德》（粤版）七年级上册主编；《廉洁修身》（初中版）教材主编。邝教授研究方向为中学政治课程与教学论，主讲《中学政治教育研究》、《中学政治教学论》、《中学思想政治教学技能训练》等</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">门硕士课程、教育硕士课程；曾荣获全国首届教育硕士优秀教师，华南师范大学教学改革一等奖和教学工作优秀奖。出版了个人专著</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">部、合著</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">部、编著</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">部、主编和参编教材</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">7</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">部；在《教育研究》、《课程·教材·教法》等权威刊物、省级刊物公开发表论文</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">多篇，主持、参与教育部重大项目、国家“十五”课题、广东省“十五”规划课题</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">6</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">项。（人文系凌云志供稿）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV>', '近期工作', '学术讲座', '1', '12018112010184418_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-18 00:00:00', '116', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('274', '谢绍熺老师与国培班学员探讨新课程改革中的问题和对策', '<DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=448 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/8741811201018479_1.gif\" width=779 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">谢老师在给学员讲课</SPAN></DIV> <DIV align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.9pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.34\"><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"5\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">上午，广东省教育厅教研室主任，华南师大教育硕士导师谢绍熺特级教师受邀来国培置换班授课。人文社会科学系系主任廖建平教授主持了讲座，人文社会科学系副主任伍辉副教授和培训班班导师凌云志老师与国培班学员一起听课。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">谢老师首先从新课改的目的和任务谈起，认为简单地说</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">新课改其实就是用新课程取代旧课程，它不涉及教师聘任制度</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">学校管理体制，但不能简单地归结为只换教科书，改革的根本目的，是为了每一个学生的发展，为了中华民族的振兴！他说，课程改革的核心目标是促进学生全面而有个性的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">生动活泼的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">可持续的发展</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">着力培养学生的社会责任感</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">创新精神和实践能力；通过确立新的人才培养规格</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">改革培养方式</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">改变学生的学习方式和生存方式；提高基础教育质量水平</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">全面提高民族素质；为建设创新型国家</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">实现民族振兴</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">,</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">提供有力的人才支撑。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 17.95pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.56\"><st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"谢\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">谢</SPAN></st1:PersonName><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">老师希望我们的中学思想品德课教师能够真正构建合乎新课程标准理念的课堂教学生态，他认为可以从教学目标、教学活动主体、教学内容、课堂练习、教学过程、教学媒体和教学评价等多个方面来入手进行。<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"谢\">谢</st1:PersonName>老师特别强调要所有受训老师真正去研究新课程标准，在实际教学中贯彻新课标的新理念，切实提高思想品德课的教学实效。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">在授课过程中，<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"谢\">谢</st1:PersonName>老师还就学员们在自己教学实践中遇到的一些疑难问题进行了现场解答。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.8pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.06\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">谢绍熺简介</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">：广东省教育厅教研室主任，华南师大教育硕士导师，特级教师，中国教育学会德育专业委员会理事；广东教育学会常务理事；广东教育学会中学政治专业委员会副理事长，中学政治教研员。主编《思想品德》（粤教版）九年级教材，著有《思想政治必修</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">4—</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">政治生活》，主持广东省中小学教学研究“十一五”规划课题</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">---</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">《思想品德》课程的班级教学与个性化教学互补与协调的实践研究，在《教育创新》等杂志发表论文多篇。（人文系凌云志供稿）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>', '近期工作', '学术讲座', '1', '8741811201018479_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-18 00:00:00', '135', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('275', '“朝花夕拾，似水流年”衡阳师范学院人文系“国培”晚会圆满举行', '<DIV> <DIV> <DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/78223112010151958_1.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">晚会现场给两位学员过生日</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/78223112010151958_2.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">小品《咱也是个兵》</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/78223112010151958_3.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">舞蹈《汉风古韵》</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/78223112010151958_4.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">“国培”班老师<SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">曹彦<SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">深情献唱</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">近日，<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">国培计划——湖南省初中思想品德课骨干教师置换培训班和短期集中培训班<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN>相继在我院开班，具体培训工作由人文系组织实施。为了丰富学员们的课外生活，不仅让他们学有所成，还要在这里生活愉快，真正融入师院这个大家庭，我系领导班子积极筹备，为学员精心安排了一场以“朝花夕拾，似水流年”为主题的“国培”晚会。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\"><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"16\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>16</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">晚<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>00</SPAN>，晚会在我院东校区音乐厅拉开帷幕<SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">。出席晚会的嘉宾有继续教育学院书记申秀英教授，继续教育学院院长涂昊教授，思想品德课程教师培训学科首席专家、人文社会科学系系主任廖建平教授，人文系党总支书记廖新平副教授，人文系副主任伍辉副教授等。国培置换班和短训班学员、人文系师生到场观看了晚会。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">晚会以温情活泼的舞蹈《相亲相爱》开场，梅杰等表演的小品《咱也是个兵》，笑料迭出，让人捧腹大笑、掌声不断，重温军训生活。<SPAN lang=EN-US>T</SPAN>台秀《我们<SPAN lang=EN-US>90</SPAN>后》，创意非凡，他们将军训服改制成时下流行的款式，充满青春活力，令现场观众眼界大开。诗朗诵《园丁颂》，声情并茂，表达了对老师们奉献精神的感谢和敬意。“国培”老师</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">曹彦<SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">深情献唱一首《纽约的司机，驾着北京的梦》，歌声饱满嘹亮，台下掌声雷动。时逢国培<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"班两位\">班两位</st1:PersonName>老师同一天过生日，晚会现场还为他们准备了生日蛋糕，全场高唱生日快乐歌，将整台晚会推向了高潮。除了歌舞表演、小品等，晚会还穿插了游戏环节，尽量让观众参与进来。本场晚会举办非常成功，气氛欢快热烈，其乐融融。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">本次活动由人文社会科学系主办，人文社会科学系团总支学生分会文艺部承办。<SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN>人文系耿华玲供稿<SPAN lang=EN-US>)</SPAN></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV></DIV>', '近期工作', null, '4', '78223112010151958_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-19 00:00:00', '239', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('276', '我系长春花志愿者协会“手拉手海星大行动”成功举行', '<DIV align=center><IMG height=379 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/24025112010114439_1.gif\" width=672 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center>长春花协会全体成员</DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=455 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/24025112010114439_3.gif\" width=337 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center>长春花协会助养的孩子之一</DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=497 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/24025112010114439_4.gif\" width=346 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center>长春花协会助养的孩子之二</DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=244 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/24025112010114439_2.gif\" width=322 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 35.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">黄昏，一位年轻人漫步于沙滩上，他看到远处一位老者在不停地拾起被海水冲到岸上的海星，将它们扔到海里，于是有了下面一段对话：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">“老先生，您为什么要花这么大的力气做这无谓的事情？”<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.3pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">“当明天太阳出来的时候，这颗海星就会死。”<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">“每天都有无数海星被冲上岸来，难道您都将他们拾起来扔到海里去吗？”<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.3pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">“我至少可以救这一颗海星。”</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.4pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">年轻人不语，也蹲下身来拾起一颗海星向海里扔去。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.4pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 35.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">为了给那些福利院的孩子提供一点点的帮助，为了让更多的人关注到那些因残疾或疾病而被家人无情抛弃的孩子。我们人文系长春花青年志愿者协会的志愿者们走进了衡阳市福利院，并为帮助那里的残障儿童们举行了一次全院级的“手拉手海星大行动”。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 35.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">活动时间从</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">日持续到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">日，其中音乐系小百灵青协和湖南工学院爱心小屋一起参与到活动中来。活动时间长，影响力大是对这次活动最贴切的形容。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 35.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">这次活动以每班每月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">元助养小孩的活动形式为主，另有义卖福利院孩子们亲手制作的手工艺品，以及派志愿者深入寝室募捐衣物。班级助养这方面也取得了圆满的成功。我系大一大二大三共</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">个班全部参加助养。而小百灵志愿者协会更发动了音乐系</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">16</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">个班级参加助养。共筹得助养费近</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">5000</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">元。其中，义卖手工艺品</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">550 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">元，效果相当不错。志愿者自发募捐现金</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\"> <SPAN lang=EN-US>230</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">多元。此外湖南工学院爱心小屋也取得了一定成就。这是我们志愿者辛苦努力取得的成功，体现了我们青年志愿者的奉献精神。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 35.5pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">通过这次活动，我们给福利院的孩子们在物质和精神上都提供了很大的帮助，终于将每份小小的爱心汇聚成了爱的海洋。而我们的志愿者们在这个过程中体会到了关爱他人的那种快乐。同时这次活动也点起了关注国际关心中国慈善协会里的残障孤儿们第一把火，让更多人把目光放到弱势群体的身上来</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">! <o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"宋体, MS Song\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">爱人者，人恒爱之。爱没有界限，予人玫瑰，手留余香。付出一份爱心，收获一份快乐，我们的爱心和真情，会是他们寒冷冬日里的一抹温暖。这个冬天，他们因我们而不再孤单！（人文系供稿）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', '学生工作', '学生社团', '4', '24025112010114439_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-25 00:00:00', '143', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('277', '“国培计划”（2010）湖南省初中思想品德骨干教师短期培训班学员聚餐活动顺利举行', '<DIV align=center><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/5022511201012108_1.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center>各位领导和学员共进晚餐</DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/5022511201012108_2.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center>学员向张登玉副院长敬酒</DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">光阴似箭，日月如梭。<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN>日，为期<SPAN lang=EN-US>14</SPAN>天的湖南省初中思想品德骨干教师国培短训班即将结束，临别之际，人文社会科学系特别在大众酒楼为国培班学员举行了一次聚餐活动。参加聚餐的领导有副院长<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"张登玉\">张登玉</st1:PersonName>教授，继续教育学院书记<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"申秀英\">申秀英</st1:PersonName>教授、院长涂昊教授，人文社会科学系党总支书记廖新<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"平副\">平副</st1:PersonName>教授、主<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"任廖建平\">任廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授、副主<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"任唐林生\">任唐林生</st1:PersonName>教授、副主<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"任伍辉副\">任伍辉副</st1:PersonName>教授等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">22</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">日晚上，大众酒楼内灯火辉煌、觥筹交错，学员们边吃边聊，畅谈学习体会和收获。进餐中间，学员们纷纷举杯，向张登玉副院长、廖新平书记、廖建平主任等领导敬酒，表达他们的感谢、感激之情。整个聚餐活动气氛融洽，温暖感人，大家的感情也在不断加深。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">张副院长对我系承办的这次培训工作给予了充分肯定。他认为，在人文社会科学系的精心组织下，本次培训构建了科学的课程体系，组织了优秀的专家团队，配备了精干的后勤服务工作人员，工作非常出色，使学员们在衡阳师院不仅学有所获，而且生活愉快。整个培训环境和谐、气氛融洽、管理到位、成果显著，达到了预期的目标，做到了多方满意，起到了引领示范的作用。（人文社会科学系耿华玲供稿）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', '近期工作', null, '2', '5022511201012108_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-25 00:00:00', '195', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('278', '国培计划（2010）衡阳师范学院初中思想品德骨干教师短期培训班圆满结业', '<DIV align=center><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/1162511201012164_1.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center>结业典礼现场</DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/1162511201012164_2.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><FONT face=Tahoma color=#2b2b2b>副院长张登玉教授出席典礼并讲话</FONT></DIV> <DIV align=center><FONT face=Tahoma color=#2b2b2b></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=514 src=\"http://renwen.hynu.cn/uppic/1162511201012164_3.gif\" width=682 align=middle border=1></DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p><FONT size=4>结业典礼现场</FONT></P></o:p></SPAN> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=center><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" IsROCDate=\"False\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" Day=\"23\" Month=\"11\" Year=\"2010\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>23</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">上午，由人文社会科学系承办的“国培计划”（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>）初中思想品德课骨干教师短期培训班结业典礼在衡阳市委党校举行。典礼由人文社会科学系廖新平书记主持。副院长张登玉教授，思想品德课课程学科首席专家、人文社会科学系主任廖建平教授，继续教育学院院长涂昊教授，人文社会科学系副主任唐林生教授、伍辉副教授等出席了典礼。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">副院长<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"张登玉\">张登玉</st1:PersonName>教授代表学院发表讲话，他首先代表学院向关心、支持、指导本次培训工作的各级领导和专家致以诚挚的谢意，向来自全省<SPAN lang=EN-US>14</SPAN>个市州、取得优异成绩的湖湘初中思想品德教师表示热烈的祝贺，向为本次培训工作付出辛勤劳动的全体工作人员表示衷心的感谢。张院长说，大家的共同努力下，我们精心打造了一支高水平的培训专家团队，力邀了全国知名的思想品德教育教学专家和一批敬业奉献、造诣颇深的初中思想品德特级教师，让广大的参训学员有机会与梦寐以求的教学名师面对面地进行交流，真正起到了引领示范的作用。根据培训的特点和要求，我们制订了切实可行的培训管理制度和学员评价办法，并认真组织实施。在为期十四天的培训过程中，人文社会科学系组织外请专家、本系教师、中学一线教师共同努力，对新课标进行了解读；较系统地学习了现代教育理念和素质教育的主要精神；讲授了课堂教学艺术和各个教学环节的应对技巧、处理技巧；还进行了教学实践考察活动；外请专家从更高层次上揭示了思想品德课教学的发展趋势、新课改以及有效教学等理论和实践问题。在二十多个单元的培训中始终坚持以学科为基础，以问题为中心，以案例为载体，紧密联系实际，有针对性地提高大家的教学能力和教学水平。整个培训环境和谐、气氛融洽、管理到位、成果显著。达到了预期目标，做到了多方满意，起到了引领方向、示范方法、促进改革的作用，为下阶段的培训工作带了好头，也为衡阳师范学院培训特色品牌的打造进一步奠定了基础。然后，张院长还对受训教师提出了几点希望。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">思想品德课学科首席专<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"家廖建平\">家廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授就本次培训作了总结。<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"廖\">廖</st1:PersonName>教授说，在培训过程中，所有受训教师通过基本理论辅导、组织参观考察、开展岗位实践，强化了基本功，打牢了当好思想品德教师的根基，进一步树立了正确的学科思想，提高了思想政治素养，增强了品德修养，拓宽了知识结构，丰富了教学能力。<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"廖\">廖</st1:PersonName>教授希望大家通过培训学习，理论视野更开阔，教学理念更清晰，科研方向更明确，确实达到思想积淀、经验积累、能力积蓄、根底积厚的良好效果。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">继续教育学院院长涂昊博士随后发表讲话，他认为在培训首席专<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"家廖建平\">家廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授的精心安排下，本次培训构建了科学合理的课程体系，组织了优秀的专家团队，配备了精干的后勤服务工作组，培训办得非常出色，使学员们在衡阳师院不仅学有所获，而且生活愉快。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">来自益阳沅江政通学校的<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"余红英\">余红英</st1:PersonName>老师代表学员讲话。<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"余\">余</st1:PersonName>老师首现简要回顾了十五天短暂而宝贵的培训生活，她代表所有受训教师感谢衡阳师院为他们提供的好的学习平台，感谢所有授课专家无私的奉献，感谢人文社会科学系的老师和同学提供的热心和周到的服务。她随后满含深情地说，在此次的学习过程中，所有受训老师收获了知识，收获了友谊，也收获了一段重要的人生经历。她表示将在未来的教育教学工作中，真正地贯彻素质教育的精神，真正地把新的教育观念和思想落实到实践中去。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #2b2b2b; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">随后，在主席台就座的领导和专家向全体学员颁发了结业证书，并向优秀学员颁发了荣誉证书。（人文社科系凌云志供稿）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', '近期工作', null, '3', '1162511201012164_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-11-25 00:00:00', '206', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('279', '爱我雁城，爱我师院——人文系打响校园“畅通、整洁、绿化”三大工程攻坚战', '<DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=523 src=\"uppic/82610122010175945_1.gif\" width=694 align=middle border=1></DIV> <DIV>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center>&nbsp;</DIV> <DIV align=center><IMG height=392 src=\"uppic/82610122010175945_2.gif\" width=521 align=middle border=1></DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">11</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">月下旬，“落实政府三大工程动员会议精神，创建畅通、整洁、绿化衡阳师院”专题会议在我院东校区学术交流中心六楼学术报告厅举行。为此，我院还专门制定了《衡阳师范学院关于开展城市“三大工程”活动实施方案》。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">为了更好地落实学院“三大工程”活动实施方案，建设一个和谐、舒适的绿色校园，<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate Year=\"2010\" Month=\"12\" Day=\"3\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>日下午</st1:chsdate>，人文系学生在党总支的组织下，自带工具在我院东校区文综楼打扫卫生。学生们下课后来到文综楼，他们扫的扫，擦的擦，拣的拣，忙得热火朝天。大家一共刷洗了<SPAN lang=EN-US>13</SPAN>间教室，<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>层楼道，清扫了文综楼周围的垃圾。经过近两个小时的辛勤劳动，白色垃圾不见了，教室里、讲台上、桌椅上的灰尘没有了，文综楼里外焕然一新。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">教室是学生开展学习活动的重要场所，教室的卫生直接影响到学生的身体健康、教师的教学效果。人文系学生此次开展的打扫活动，为大家营造了一个良好的学习环境，也督促大家日后养成良好的卫生习惯，爱护我们的校园环境，为建设生态宜居的衡阳以及生态园林式的绿色师院而共同努力。（人文系供稿）</SPAN></P></DIV>', '学生工作', null, '2', '82610122010175945_1.gif', '人文社会科学系', '2010-12-10 00:00:00', '129', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('280', '人文社会科学系系务公开实施细则', '<DIV> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">建立和健全系务公开制度是做好系务公开的基础和前提，我系从实际出发，做到统一领导，分工负责，责任明确，并在实际工作中不断健全和完善工作机制，加强对系务公开的真实性、及时性和实效性等进行监督检查。根据《衡阳师范学院校务公开实施办法》，结合我系实际，特制订系务公开实施细则。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一、</SPAN> </B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">系务公开的指导思想</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">实施系务公开，必须以毛泽东思想、邓小平理论、“三个代表”重要思想为指导，深入贯彻落实科学发展观和党的十七大精神，坚持党的社会主义民主政治建设的基本方向，以增加系务公开的透明度，通过全面推行系务公开制度，进一步完善以二级教代会为基本形式的民主参与、民主管理、民主监督机制，增强系师生的民主意识，系管理干部的服务意识，提高工作质量与效率，密切党群、干群关系，推进我系党风廉政建设和民主政治建设，促进我系的改革、发展和稳定。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二、系务公开的基本原则</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（一）依法公开，责任明确。系务公开必须依照国家法律、法规和有关政策规定进行，实行“谁领导谁负责”的制度。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（二）实事求是，注重实效。系务公开的内容必须真实可靠、详细具体，公开的内容和形式必须有利于教师的民主参与和民主监督，有利于系的改革、发展和稳定，要讲求实效，不搞形式主义。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（三）结合实际，突出重点，系务公开必须从本系实际出发，重点抓住涉及系发展的重大决策、事关教师切身利益的问题，教师关注的热点、难点问题，系领导干部的廉政自律情况等。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（四）方便教师，有利监督。系务公开要方便教师知情，方便教师办事，有利于教师行使监督权，要强化教师对系管理干部的有效监督。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">三、系务公开的组织领导</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">系务公开必须形成由系领导主抓，教师共同监督，广大教师和学生积极参与的领导体制和工作机制，要把系务公开工作列入日常工作基本程序，促进系公开工作的主动性和积极性。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">成立系务公开工作小组。组长由系党总支书记廖新平担任，副组长由系主<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:PersonName ProductID=\"任廖建平\" w:st=\"on\">任廖建平</st1:PersonName>教授担任，成员由系副主<st1:PersonName ProductID=\"任唐林生\" w:st=\"on\">任唐林生</st1:PersonName>教授、<st1:PersonName ProductID=\"伍辉副\" w:st=\"on\">伍辉副</st1:PersonName>教授、办公室主任耿华玲以及教师代表组成。工作小组制定系务公开工作计划，安排部署并指导全系的系务公开工作；审定系务公开的内容、范围、程序，检查系务公开的实施情况；接受全系师生的监督，注意听取各方面的意见，及时进行总结，积极有效地开展工作。系务公开工作小组设办公室，负责日常事务的处理。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">系里定时向学院校务公开工作小组汇报工作进展情况。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">四、系务公开的内容</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（一）有关系发展的重大决策，包括系发展目标、规划、年度工作计划、年终工作总结等。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（二）有关系重大改革措施，包括教学、管理、校内岗位津贴改革方案等。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（三）系人事工作，包括教师、干部晋级、晋职、人员调入调出、公派出国、进修访问、专业技术评聘等。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（四）教职工奖惩。各类先进的评选名额、评选条件、结果、奖惩办法、年度考核、违纪处理办法。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（五）系规章制度的制定、修改、贯彻执行。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（六）系物资采购，包括办公用品，教学用品、设备、图书资料、教材等。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（七）系财务管理、收支情况。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（八）教职工及学生党员发展公示。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（九）学生管理。包括学生奖学金、贷学金、特困生补助发放、评优、出国、违纪处理等。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（十）领导干部廉洁自律各项规定执行情况，党风廉政建设责任制执行情况。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（十一）其他涉及师生利益的重要事项。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">五、系务公开的形式</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（一）代表大会形式。通过定期召开系教代会、学代会，讨论审议有关方案、办法、计划等，进行系务公开。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（二）在本系网站设立系务公开栏，设立系务信箱，建立信息反馈和监督系统。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（三）会议形式。通过全系教职工大会、教研组会议、学生大会、座谈会等形式公开系务。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">（四）设立系务公开栏，作为系务公开的的基本窗口。</SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><STRONG><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></STRONG><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">人文社会科学系</SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" align=right><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"></SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日</SPAN></P></DIV>', '规章制度', null, '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2010-12-19 00:00:00', '52', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('281', '人文社会科学系年度考核实施细则', '<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">一、总则</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">为确立本系教学工作的中心地位，强化教师教学工作职责和质量意识，突出教师教学工作业绩和科研水平在教师职务晋升、岗位聘任、奖惩中的重要性，使教师教学工作业绩和科研水平考核规范化、制度化、科学化，根据学院相关规定，特制定本系年度考核细则。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">本办法适用于本系全体教职员工。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">本系成立专门的考核领导小组，领导小组由系党政主要负责人组成。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">二、考核基本原则</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">　　</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">公开、公平、公正原则。考核应客观公正、民主公开、注重实绩。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">　　</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">2.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">三结合原则。领导考核、群众评议与个人总结相结合。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">　　</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">3.</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">定性与定量结合原则。定性考核与定量考核相结合。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">三、考核办法与程序</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、教师每年度考核一次，其中教学效果的评价是教师教学工作业绩的考核重点。学生评价作为教师教学效果评价的重要依据之一，教学督导及专家对教师课堂教学质量测评也是教师考核的重要依据之一。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、考核小组对教师的教学工作量、教学效果、教学建设、教学研究与改革和教师教书育人等情况进行审核后，确定考核等级。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、考核结果由系主任向本人反馈。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">四、考核内容</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">考核内容包括德、能、勤、绩四个方面，重点考核工作实绩。德，主要考核政治、思想表现和职业道德表现。能，主要考核业务技术水平，业务能力的提高、知识更新情况。勤，主要考核工作态度、敬业精神和遵守劳动纪律情况。绩，主要考核履行职责、完成工作任务的质量、数量、效果，取得的成果水平及社会效益和经济效益情况。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、重点考核教学工作业绩。主要包括教学工作量、教学效果、教学建设、改革与研究、教书育人等方面。其中，教学工作量主要包括由学院安排的、在人才培养方案内的教师讲授和辅导的课程以及承担的实践性教学的工作量；教学效果主要包括教师在承担课程、实践性教学等方面的评价效果；教学建设、改革与研究主要包括教师承担的教学建设与研究项目、教学研究论文论著（教材）等。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、教师工作业绩考核实行等级考核制，分为优秀、称职、基本称职、不称职四个等级，并进行比例控制，优秀比例控制在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">20</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">％以内。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">各等级大致要求如下：优秀：教师在评价年度的教学工作量、教学效果、教学改革与研究、教书育人等方面中至少在某一方面表现突出，教学工作量饱满，每年度至少主讲一门课程，所主讲的课程教学质量综合测评优秀，未出现教学事故。称职：教师在评价年度的教学工作量、教学效果、教学改革与研究、教书育人等方面中至少在某一方面表现比较突出，教学工作量符合规定要求，每年度至少主讲一门课程，所主讲课程教学质量综合测评良好以上，未出现教学事故。基本称职：教师在教学工作量、教学效果、教学改革与研究、教书育人等方面表现一般，在某些方面尚需改进和提高或出现过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">次一般教学事故，教学工作量基本符合规定要求。不称职：教师在评价年度的教学工作量、教学效果、教学改革与研究、教书育人等方面中在某一方面表现明显不足或有下列情况之一者：受党内严重警告或政纪记大过以上处分；教学工作量没有达到学院规定要求；出现教书育人中影响恶劣事件；出现一般教学事故</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">次以上（含</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">次），或严重教学事故</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">次以上（含</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">次）；无正当理由拒不承担学院安排的教学任务；教学质量综合测评明显偏低；违反计划生育政策；连续旷工</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">天或累计旷工</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">10</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">天以上。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、党政管理人员的考核重点为廉洁自律、政策水平、工作能力、工作态度、工作作风、协作精神、工作实绩等情况。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">五、考核结果的使用</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、专职教师考核结果由学院职能部门记入教师本人业务档案，考核结果作为教师评优、岗位聘任、职称评定、津贴和奖金发放的重要依据。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">教学工作业绩考核结果基本称职或不称职者，由本系党政领导向教师本人发出通知，提出改进要求。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;人</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">文社会科学系</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P> <P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2009</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">12</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\">15</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">日</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', '规章制度', null, '0', null, '人文社会科学系', '2010-12-19 00:00:00', '42', '0');
